{
  "abstract": "Facing the challenges of an increasing world population, a\r\nchanging climate and ever depleting resources, agricultural\r\nis one of the few options for meeting the demand of food security. It is necessary to\r\napply a dynamic and systematic approach to effectively manage\r\nthe complex agri-eco production and green processing\r\nsystems. Indeed, farming systems approach for appropriate\r\ntechnology development and simulation modeling is a result\r\nof adopting the system thinking by the agricultural research community...",
